summary: Reaction: When You Surprise Them At Work
title: Reaction: When You Surprise Them At Work
body:
Group: BTS
Genre: Fluff, Comedy
Word Count: 77

Jin: Looks in the mirror to make sure he looks good.

Yoongi: Stops what ever he is doing.

Hoseok: Yells at his members “My girlfriend is better than yours!”

Namjoon: He would just open his arms for you to run into.

Jimin: He wouldn’t know how to react and gets all shy.

Taehyung: He would run to you picking you up “Jagi! What are you doing here?!”

Jungkook: He’s happy to see you and can’t stop smiling.

—-Admin JordiRebel—-
